description:

Most effective social networking appearances with the turnover time of just 24 hours*!

What is included in the social networking package?
We will provide a professional and attractive looking Facebook page for your company/organisation/individual along with a twitter page and tumblr blog pre-loaded with tweets and posts of images and information that you have provided us with that you would like to promote and we will do so in the most effective fashion.

How does it work? 
You purchase the social networking package here and once purchased send us an email (conceptukcontact@googlemail.com) specifying every detail of the pages you would like to be included and any designs you may have in mind etc. feel free to include images and other media you think may be of assistance.
